  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK762">
<l>ulaiviṭat tūṟañcā vaṉkaṇ ṭolaiviṭattut</l>
<l>tolpaṭaik kallā laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ancient army can alone have the valour which makes it stand by its king at the time of defeat, fearless of wounds and unmindful of its reduced strength.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
